==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Orpin
<hw>Or"pin</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F., orpiment, also, the plant
orpine. See <er>Orpiment</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A yellow pigment
of various degrees of intensity, approaching also to red.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>The orpine.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>orpine</ent>⟦br⟧
